message.body: I only drove by it briefly but I saw this skate spot with a bunch of ramps and shit under the trestle on 9th st. Somewhere between Fairmount and Cecile B. Moore. You ever check that out?
Yea, it's 9th and poplar. Ny the church with the gold dome.
I suppose. I wasn't really paying attention to that cuz I was looking for an address to make a delivery but could be. You would probably know better than me.
